Interface Item

All Known Implementing Classes:
Carrot, Coral, DecorItem, Fish, FoodItem, GiftItem, MessageInBottle, Pearl, PineappleHouse, Sandcastle, Shrimp, TreasureChest
public interface Item
Item interface.

The Item interface provides a general format for each of the item subclasses (FoodItem, DecorItem, GiftItem). It has methods useItem, buyItem and getPrice which are useful to all implementing classes.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Cadence Megan McGillicuddy
